code: @Override public void channelRead(final ChannelHandlerContext ctx, final Object msg) throws Exception {     if (msg instanceof AbstractMessage) {         final AbstractMessage amsg = (AbstractMessage) msg.         final Cause cause = amsg.getHeader().getCauseOfTransmission().getCause().         if (this.discards.contains(cause)) {             LOG.debug("Discarding: {}", cause).             return.         }     }     super.channelRead(ctx, msg). }
